    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      APP_OFFLINE
      Constant used in routing response which indicates that the route cannot be calculated because the application is offline.
      INTERNAL_ERROR
      Constant used in routing response which indicates that the route cannot be calculated because of an internal error.
      INTERNET_IS_TURNED_OFF

      • APP_OFFLINE

        public static final SKRouteListener.SKRoutingErrorCode APP_OFFLINE
        Constant used in routing response which indicates that the route cannot be calculated because the application is offline. This would happen in the case of online routing when the application was turned to offline mode.

      • INTERNET_IS_TURNED_OFF

        public static final SKRouteListener.SKRoutingErrorCode INTERNET_IS_TURNED_OFF
        Constant used in routing response which indicates that the route cannot be calculated because the internet is turned off. This would happen in the case of online routing when the client turns off the internet connection on the device.
